Event - Class in edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner
This class represents an event of a vacation, which are contained inside an array list of events for each vacation as one of the fields.
Event(String, String, String) - Constructor for class edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.Event
This is the constructor for an event object, which cannot be instantiated, but takes on three parameters common to all types of events: name, date, and time
EVENT_KEY - Static variable in class edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.VacationsMainActivity
Similar to the main activity, this event key is used to identify the event that was passed from the list view of events.
EventListAdapter - Class in edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner
This class is used to adapt our Array List of events to our list view in the Vacations Main Activity class to provide an accurate and updated version of our event list every time.
